{"tid":1725408,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想學好英文有咩好方法？","createTime":"2019-11-15T17:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T05:52:48.000Z","uid":293638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca2a606ce3f7b52e580a5a7fcb669c81bf8f27c","tid":1725408,"uid":293638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a6dc98773cd0dc06471fdab10edef1571466c6","tid":1725408,"uid":132397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"我都想知"},{"pid":"41bdcd3c76bd3a1e4b1e06e6683c8f0ac6d93c3a","tid":1725408,"uid":78255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:42:46.000Z","msg":"煲劇 但唔係睇住中文字幕嚟睇 睇英文字幕<br />\n嘗試理解吓佢點組句子 點樣用字<br />\n咁樣學會易上手好多"},{"pid":"f203e5810f12b65c4abe369c351e6eac3c0bd995","tid":1725408,"uid":78255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:44:54.000Z","msg":"一開始唔建議睇文睇書 一來字都唔識多隻睇嚟冇意思 二來全文字真係比較悶 好難提起興趣<br />\n小朋友我建議睇卡通 大人建議自己搵美劇嚟睇<br />\n<br />\n開始掌握到英文嘅思維再學grammar同學作文會易上手好多"},{"pid":"6d6420b104dc0f03b5431e31d3041026298d66d1","tid":1725408,"uid":78255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:49:59.000Z","msg":"另外睇美劇想學得快 我會建議將同一隻睇無數次睇到試背<br />\n嗰效果會突飛猛進 因為你識背 就自然思維模式與英文接軌 你會知道呢句嘅意思同埋英文嘅講法 久而久之慢慢儲到各式各樣嘅說法同生字 當然生字都係要靠記 但用睇劇睇戲去記會易啲係因為你有情節做back up 你會將呢個字同腦海中嘅情節扣連埋 你會對於佢嘅意思有更深印象"},{"pid":"2a07bac55b22f748462803099653949b8e5e01bb","tid":1725408,"uid":78255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:55:34.000Z","msg":"但如果英文有一定基礎 姐係識讀識寫識講大部分日常生活所需嘅英文 亦都寫到一篇中規中矩嘅文章 想更上一層樓就要睇書 但開始可以睇新聞 BBC/CNN/New York Times/Times呢啲都夠你地睇 呢啲文章都係比較社會性嘅用字<br />\n如果要用英文寫故事呢方面我唔熟因為我都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我平時都係睇開新聞社論就算 好少睇故事書"},{"pid":"93c7466006ec50349c99933b99076dfdc48a6e39","tid":1725408,"uid":333907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"Watch something that you are interested (e.g. TV dramas, sports, documentaries&hellip;) with English subtitles.  Focus on listening the conversation/boardcast and use the subtitles to supplement your understanding.  Grammar and writing will come later when you start reading news journals and literatures."},{"pid":"fa1c1cc4c8034d350697c79820c065b1486191f6","tid":1725408,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T23:42:04.000Z","msg":"秒經post<br />\n你去Google search下啲舊post<br />\n好多人都講過好多有用嘅方法"},{"pid":"a717d614c5f1c0b383fd4d7d9711d330cf45c15e","tid":1725408,"uid":336046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T00:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe69f059841ecd9af157e8c04867e4326d062f3b","tid":1725408,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"步驟:<br />\n1. 流利正確讀到英文單字同淺易文章<br />\n2. 睇中英對照文章或新聞學英文表達<br />\n3. 多聽真實英語鍛煉聽力並口語表達<br />\n4. 多睇英文書積極查字典學新vocab<br />\n<br />\n你有心學，我免費教。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/GLHHLG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGLHHLG&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BCLieoVo5Z%2Bt8AyiqwqBN0Y%3D&h=155e3032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/GLHHLG</a>"}]}